Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(960,100)\fad(600,600)}翻譯+校對+部分時間軸：nkknspkk @色花堂\N感謝論壇網友BillieEilish提供的部分時間軸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:12.46,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,我是進這個公司已經8年的上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:23.97,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,雖然工齡很長了但是工作上的失誤還是很多 總是被上司罵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:34.65,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,工作不順個人生活現在也是一個人...當然女朋友更是沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,牛島先生 抱歉打擾您工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這份文件麻煩您看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這個資料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,根據現在的資料來看的話 上一次的資料也是上升的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為未來的結算資料可能會上升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,現在說不定還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.25,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那就照你說的來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在這方面你挺擅長的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:43.35,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,上原小姐真厲害啊...明明是才進公司2年的後輩 工作卻很出色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,現在發表上個月的銷售資料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,第一名是齊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今後也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是很嚴峻的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一股腦兒的完成了目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這個月是年度結算的時刻 我會更加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的呢 接下來就拜託你了  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來就是~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上原
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-在  -就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上個月的資料就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起 你真的很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止重複的相同團隊工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,重新評估資料後我認為改進會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是上原對於細微的資料很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今後也要更加努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大家向這兩位學習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了 向這兩位學習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是銷售額低下的這幾位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這幾個人 真的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:12.34,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,部長的牢騷又開始了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡確定沒錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,82)}（上原和齊藤討論工作中...）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像有點健忘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:04:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,82)}（齊藤討論前段時間去的客戶那邊發生的趣事...）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:56.78,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,銷售業績第一名的齊藤和第二名的上原...看起來關係很好呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:10.80,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的“天生一對”吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢？明明已經很努力的跑業績了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 什麼叫很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你盡是去睡覺和打柏青哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事說出來合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事我要告訴部長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,擼管的店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有中午才出勤 原來是去找高級女孩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,誰告訴你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是你說的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事你別聲張出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的把柄被這傢伙抓住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,傻逼 不是這回事好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,外出跑業務的時候去 不合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為繪裡醬是夜間學生 只有中午才能出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是叫繪裡醬啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘿嘿 我也去這家店玩玩吧  -別啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你上個月業績也很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是去搞啥玩意兒了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.24,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也並沒有怎麼偷懶呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起來應該能完成一單的 結果還是不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 難道你也去風俗店了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,下次也給我介紹下你去的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 真厲害啊 上個月他也是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-他們好像在交往呢  -真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-果然是這樣啊  -當然是的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的？我喜歡上原小姐的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 工作出色 又很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-真想和她交往呢  -完全想不出她私下裡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大概 那種女人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛超激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然還是這個屌樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為你盡說這些蠢話 業績才上不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也是往這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.37,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,是的 你也是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是第一次一起下班回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.04,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,話說天氣變得冷起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.71,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:22.15,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,上個月的銷售額 你真的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.86,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,啊？你的目標是第一名啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然是的啊 既然要做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.20,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天我要超過齊藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.93,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,我？？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.55,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,馬馬虎虎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得前輩應該能做的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能注意到誰都沒有注意到的細節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,非常重要的事情也很上心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說前輩...在跑業務的時候去吃喝或者打柏青哥了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:14.06,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,我才沒做那種事呢 偶爾會去喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喝茶？好可愛！喝茶的話我也是會去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.08,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然的了 我也是會去休閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 養精蓄銳也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這個月 還有下個月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:46.20,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,那麼 我是往這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,突然說這種話可能很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我 一直 很久之前就喜歡上前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:44.55,Default - 4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,624)}突然的告白 我當然也是說“好啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:10:02.95,Default - 5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,616)}試著交往後 她...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,572)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 80 0 80
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,560)}本以為是冷豔且一本正經的職業女性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:40.22,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,也有天真爛漫的一面 沒想到是這樣直爽的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.04,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(912,430)}好可愛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:12.22,Default - 5,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,635)}只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:26.40,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,為什麼會喜歡上這樣無精打采的我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:38.69,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,完全不明白她為什麼會喜歡上我 也沒有問她的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.91,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586,388)}要 吃 嗎 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.12,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,512)}怎 麼 樣 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.67,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(675,509)}好 吃 嗎 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.80,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,516)}是我的呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.06,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,472)}人家一直
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.06,Default - 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(748,528)}都很期待草莓的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:28.59,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:28.59,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,這次我來問問關於喜歡上我的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩好差勁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 會做夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 做夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就算做夢 醒來後也基本忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記的話和沒做過夢一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚夢到前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-關於我的？  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-誒？變大了？  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是單純變大的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩像巨人一樣變大 變成了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那是啥玩意兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 大家都被巨大的壞傢伙踩踏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是在我上面倒下的 為什麼只有我留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼奇怪的夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 仔細看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩用了最後的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣 用盡了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓我不被毀滅 保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是啥玩意兒啊 然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊 太突兀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是很突兀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 還是很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 選擇我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼和我交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩討厭我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 完全不討厭 非常喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對於瑞穂來說 比我好的人多的一批
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟你很受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我覺得前輩就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼喜歡前輩 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,直到前輩明白為止 這就當作秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩好像快睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎？一直是這個臉色啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,擺出這張臉的話部長又要生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法的事啦 就是這張臉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我來叫醒你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-好疼...  -起床啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,醒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,醒不來啦！很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話能醒來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！等下...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,醒來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？算是吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 這裡是公司 被誰看見的話怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,被人看見我無所謂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩太過在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩？久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 部長 我們去出差了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-投訴的事就拜託你了  -是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就算出錯誤也不要拉上原的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟上原比你的能力強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,部長別這樣 這次不是我的客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力協助前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-是嗎？ -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙不行的時候幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這工作以後會變得越來越重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,明白不？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-明白  -是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明天晚上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-好  -我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這是第一次和前輩一起出差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-以前有過嗎？  -不是的吧 應該是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-有點小激動呢  -為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是都外嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細想想的話不就和旅行一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,白癡 這可不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這我當然知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的公司的部長是個很難搞的客戶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 前輩的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,別說的這麼輕鬆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,反正今天還不用工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,為了迎接明天我們吃點好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,吃什麼呢？我好想吃拉麵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-啊？應該吃烤雞雜串吧  -烤雞雜串啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也覺得好吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是很好吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子好飽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來明天的工作應該會順利的 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 果然還是想吃拉麵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,拉麵是不行的吃了會嘴臭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘴巴會變臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩要喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,被人看見的話 就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,被人看見？這裡只有我和前輩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,話是這麼說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以坐在你身邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,能和前輩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這是因為前輩和我在同公司同部門才能做到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,普通的情侶就沒法做到這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也親親我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,說真的 為什麼選擇我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還在說這種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過 像你這樣的美女 和我在一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以說是太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩覺得我在說謊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,認為我是玩弄前輩的壞女人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒這樣想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就已經能明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.49,0:24:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡前輩的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.85,0:24:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,給我好好想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.53,0:24:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要對前輩這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.64,0:25:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.02,0:26:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.15,0:26:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不是公司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.68,0:26:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我們兩個人不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.31,0:26:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.40,0:27:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上說不要 前輩不也硬了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.48,0:27:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.77,0:28:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣舔啊舔我也變得舒服了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.11,0:28:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話你也變得想要爽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.93,0:29:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 你爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.48,0:29:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.02,0:31:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.59,0:32:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來做舒服的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.88,0:32:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也摸摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.15,0:32:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-這樣嗎？  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.33,0:32:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.17,0:33:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.08,0:33:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.44,0:36:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.80,0:36:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.62,0:38:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很軟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.06,0:38:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我要脫掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.55,0:38:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.22,0:39:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.13,0:39:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.60,0:39:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-這裡舒服嗎？  -好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.24,0:40:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.20,0:40:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我會越來越興奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.89,0:40:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.02,0:41:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.00,0:41:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.44,0:41:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.13,0:41:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.24,0:41:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-這裡嗎？  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.77,0:42:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-這裡也舒服吧？  -非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.44,0:43:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.44,0:45:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 到你明白為止要繼續加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.02,0:46:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.06,0:46:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.97,0:46:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,相當的舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.13,0:46:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.98,0:46:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.88,0:47:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.31,0:47:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎 前輩  -很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.13,0:47:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一起更舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.80,0:47:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.48,0:47:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.04,0:48:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎  -很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.62,0:48:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.80,0:48:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,又要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.31,0:48:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.24,0:49:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫蕩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.71,0:49:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-能看見嗎前輩  -啊 能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.22,0:49:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 讓我再看清楚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.91,0:49:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很下流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.15,0:50:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.77,0:50:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.46,0:51:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好深啊 插好深啊 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.15,0:51:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.11,0:51:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.20,0:52:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這次我要老漢推車了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.97,0:53:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.37,0:53:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.70,0:53:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要插的更深哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.12,0:53:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 啊 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.46,0:53:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再深一點可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.35,0:53:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.73,0:54:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我...被前輩插入的地方很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.91,0:54:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.11,0:54:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.86,0:54:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.42,0:57:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.00,0:57:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-好爽  -好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.64,0:57:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.84,0:58:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.17,0:58:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 流了好多汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.33,0:58:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.33,0:59:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.28,0:59:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.39,0:59:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴裡 請射在我嘴裡
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.31,0:59:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.48,0:59:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.22,0:59:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.82,0:59:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 前輩！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.07,1:01:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.87,1:01:36.84,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,第二天...去了對方公司...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.95,1:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,關於您這邊的投訴
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.40,1:03:05.17,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,82)}（上原努力解決客戶投訴中...）
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.17,1:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 能麻煩你拿一下資料嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.57,1:03:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.72,1:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪一個來著？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.95,1:03:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.59,1:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.54,1:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請看一下這個
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.93,1:03:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.46,1:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(960,100)\fad(600,600)}翻譯+校對+部分時間軸：nkknspkk @色花堂\N感謝論壇網友BillieEilish提供的部分時間軸
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.97,1:04:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.10,1:03:59.52,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,大家都出去跑業務了 辦公室只剩下我和她了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.92,1:04:18.90,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,她切換了開關 在辦公室上開始了大膽的行為
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.94,1:04:33.22,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,坦蕩的坐在部長的位置上...真擔心有誰回來
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.65,1:04:46.80,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,這樣地大膽...真擔心和她交往這件事被大家發現
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.59,1:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 不快點的話就有人來了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.17,1:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好險哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.22,1:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會有人來呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.17,1:05:31.01,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.17,1:05:31.01,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.53,1:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我在幹什麼 前輩知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.73,1:05:36.65,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.73,1:05:36.65,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.65,1:05:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡上前輩的理由
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.18,1:05:44.29,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.18,1:05:44.29,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,還不知道呢...。
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.09,1:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.24,1:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,說這種話的話
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.33,1:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要這樣了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.07,1:06:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.07,1:06:00.11,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,白癡 你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.55,1:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.55,1:06:19.22,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.73,1:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.04,1:06:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為前輩說還不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.29,1:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.29,1:06:29.40,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,這個和那個沒關係好吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.68,1:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,說還不知道的話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.79,1:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,還在說這種話的話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.81,1:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.81,1:06:48.82,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.74,1:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪前輩還不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.02,1:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人在
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.46,1:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只要前輩不發出大的聲響就不會暴露啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.20,1:07:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在同一個公司真方便呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.93,1:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.96,1:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上說不要
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.22,1:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為何這裡變得這麼硬？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.82,1:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說前輩是這種情況下會興奮的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.44,1:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 爽不爽？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.17,1:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.00,1:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好臭啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.84,1:10:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是進了衛生間 我卻是來惡作劇的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.84,1:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩被我欺負的心情怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.73,1:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來沒想要這樣惡作劇的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.94,1:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想見前輩了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.77,1:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩真的好臭啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.73,1:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.93,1:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩真的是好脹啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.64,1:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.27,1:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.73,1:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 要射了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.62,1:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,請射在我舌頭上
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.15,1:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係哦 多多射出來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.73,1:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.77,1:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.69,1:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.64,1:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.91,1:20:40.99,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.91,1:20:40.99,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,這樣子被人看見就遭了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.66,1:20:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.02,1:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不清理乾淨臉 就回去的話...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.81,1:20:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.81,1:20:58.94,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.71,1:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是工作時間 和前輩在一起真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.33,1:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來前輩要幫我擦乾淨哦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.32,1:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,78)}（開會內容就不翻譯了 無關緊要...）
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.04,1:24:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就是這麼回事 大澤 關於這個你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.28,1:24:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大澤
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.82,1:24:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.31,1:24:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.84,1:24:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不...我在
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.91,1:24:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不是說“我在”的時候吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.17,1:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是要聽聽你對這個問題的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.02,1:24:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.02,1:24:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,行了！齊藤你來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.20,1:24:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.83,1:25:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.24,1:25:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.79,1:25:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼？前輩不也在做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.37,1:25:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說是做了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.14,1:25:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只是偶爾沒關褲門而已啦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.99,1:25:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你是故意的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.38,1:25:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想著是不是在勾引我也做呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.81,1:25:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼玩意兒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.26,1:25:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種地方 而且還是在會議中
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.23,1:25:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是我搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.22,1:25:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不可能做這種事的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.80,1:26:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.15,1:26:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只剩下咱倆了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.51,1:26:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？好像是的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.67,1:26:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.49,1:26:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,搞起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.45,1:26:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.62,1:26:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才勾引的繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.52,1:26:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.03,1:26:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.88,1:26:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有人來的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.95,1:26:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.02,1:26:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種地方搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.04,1:26:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩不是有這種打算才褲門大開的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.40,1:27:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有這種事啦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.02,1:27:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 這裡變硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.47,1:27:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.49,1:27:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.82,1:27:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦 在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.15,1:27:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.52,1:27:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.23,1:27:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種地方搞會很糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.95,1:27:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡可是公司啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.67,1:27:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.44,1:28:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.74,1:28:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有人來的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.52,1:28:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.26,1:28:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上周一直很忙都沒時間看我 我很寂寞啦 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.09,1:28:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你這樣說
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.15,1:29:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩不寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.47,1:29:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.68,1:29:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡前輩的只有我一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.91,1:29:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以的吧？  -不過
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.48,1:29:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們兩個人的秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.44,1:29:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.57,1:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行啊 被你這樣摸的話
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.94,1:30:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩也摸摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.60,1:31:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩的手 好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.22,1:32:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.42,1:32:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.60,1:32:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.91,1:33:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.49,1:35:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡 舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.24,1:36:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.53,1:36:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.73,1:36:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看清楚一點
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.73,1:38:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.02,1:38:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎  -好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.62,1:38:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,腿抬起來
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.97,1:38:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翹起來
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.20,1:38:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.64,1:39:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.13,1:39:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,插的這麼深的話
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.82,1:39:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.20,1:40:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.91,1:40:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.37,1:40:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.54,1:41:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.34,1:41:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.37,1:41:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~要去了~
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.79,1:41:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,從前面讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.57,1:42:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 已經很濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.80,1:42:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭 好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.39,1:43:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.31,1:43:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 我可以高潮嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.64,1:43:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.42,1:43:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.57,1:43:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這種下流的樣子 被公司的大家看到的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.12,1:44:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要說這種惡作劇的話
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.29,1:44:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛都要看不清了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.19,1:44:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.14,1:44:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.33,1:45:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把會議室都弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.17,1:46:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.27,1:46:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好打掃的話
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.04,1:46:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,會被人發現的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.80,1:46:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以插嗎？  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.79,1:46:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.81,1:46:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.39,1:47:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 前輩也變硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.48,1:48:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.86,1:48:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.07,1:48:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,趴桌子上做做怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.84,1:49:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.42,1:49:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.42,1:50:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.17,1:50:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.66,1:50:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.24,1:50:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,插進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.28,1:51:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 插好深
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.74,1:51:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.27,1:51:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.80,1:51:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-爽不爽  -好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.77,1:52:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴裡好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.73,1:52:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.42,1:52:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.12,1:53:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.65,1:53:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.37,1:53:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.82,1:54:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好舒服啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.39,1:54:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-小穴好濕啊  -好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.40,1:54:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都是前輩讓我爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.31,1:54:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-這樣舒服嗎  -好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.97,1:54:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩對我做的所有事 都很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.98,1:55:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.79,1:56:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.87,1:56:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.22,1:57:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像快射了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.85,1:57:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 請多多射出來
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.06,1:57:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了 要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.33,1:57:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.97,1:58:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.86,1:58:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.24,1:58:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,得重新化妝才行了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.54,1:58:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是秘密哦 前輩
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.66,1:58:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.88,1:58:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.11,1:59:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,褲門關好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.07,1:59:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是故意的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.88,1:59:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,做了這種事
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.93,1:59:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,被部長看見的話怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.77,1:59:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,搞的膽戰心驚的 也不壞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.84,1:59:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.62,1:59:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.82,1:59:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不要忘了皮帶
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.88,2:00:25.60,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.88,2:00:11.82,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,今天和瑞穗一起外出跑業務
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.43,2:00:25.60,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,客戶並不怎麼感興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.86,2:00:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.42,2:00:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,下次換個計畫看看吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.28,2:00:36.41,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.28,2:00:36.41,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.95,2:00:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 前輩你餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.08,2:00:43.62,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.08,2:00:43.62,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.48,2:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是很餓了 可能是太專注了一直不停在說
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.89,2:00:50.23,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.89,2:00:50.23,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,去找點吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.31,2:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的啊 吃點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.31,2:01:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 今天前輩真帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.75,2:01:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一直是我不停的在說
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.82,2:01:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,努力學習了很多
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.57,2:01:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想著這樣才能更好的協助前輩
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.46,2:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天多虧了前輩才得救
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.91,2:01:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個企劃如果能順心的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.66,2:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩的手永遠是這樣溫暖
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.00,2:02:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我有手腳冰涼症
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.62,2:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.77,2:02:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩都流汗了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.42,2:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 乳頭變硬了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.88,2:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.02,2:04:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.40,2:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,脫下沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.73,2:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡前輩的味道了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.73,2:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有噴香水嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.31,2:07:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一直是好聞的味道
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.26,2:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,變得這麼硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.73,2:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,心跳的好快呢
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.73,2:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有人過來的話就糟糕了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.04,2:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒人會看見的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.88,2:10:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎 前輩
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.42,2:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡吃前輩的雞巴了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.06,2:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看著你舒服 我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.64,2:12:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩這裡被我吸 舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.64,2:13:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好厲害 變得越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.84,2:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,龜頭舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.75,2:14:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩的敏感點 全部告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,2:14:43.57,2:14:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,龜頭想要舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.04,2:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.20,2:15:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還是這裡？
Dialogue: 0,2:15:43.46,2:15:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.02,2:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,多多的 請多多的射出來哦
Dialogue: 0,2:18:35.97,2:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.20,2:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多哦
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.26,2:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,味道很好呢
Dialogue: 0,2:19:17.77,2:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.20,2:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩爽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.92,2:21:41.31,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.92,2:19:52.39,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,話雖如此 她喜歡我的理由到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.74,2:20:03.28,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,難道說是那件事...？
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.35,2:20:17.33,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,2年前...確實是她來我司面試的那天
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.15,2:20:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-下一個是上原瑞穗小姐 請進  -好的
Dialogue: 0,2:20:43.20,2:20:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.51,2:20:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是你掉的吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:20:47.80,2:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:50.80,2:20:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-是來面試的嗎？  -是的
Dialogue: 0,2:20:52.93,2:20:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦！
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.04,2:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.20,2:21:07.83,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,撿到了她的護身符然後打了招呼...難道說就是這件事嗎...？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.75,2:21:22.69,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,下次和瑞穗見面的時候問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.14,2:21:41.31,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:38.40,2:21:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.25,2:21:49.59,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.25,2:21:49.59,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,跟我說歡迎回來...你在我家幹什麼啊！？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.93,2:21:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼？我要住在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:52.89,2:21:57.93,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:21:52.89,2:21:57.93,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,啊！！？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:55.68,2:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我行李也帶來了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:58.06,2:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉用了你的浴巾
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.80,2:22:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,74)}注：賣還是租 沒聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.80,2:22:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己的家也賣（租）出去了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.94,2:22:13.65,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.94,2:22:13.65,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事...？
Dialogue: 0,2:22:13.15,2:22:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想和前輩一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.86,2:22:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.70,2:22:42.74,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.70,2:22:42.74,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,那個 瑞穗喜歡上我的理由 莫不是...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.51,2:22:54.79,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.51,2:22:54.79,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,瑞穗來我司面試的時候 我撿到你的護身符這件事...？
Dialogue: 0,2:22:51.37,2:22:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,正解！
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.24,2:22:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,終於回想起來了呢 前輩
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.52,2:23:01.16,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.52,2:23:01.16,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,就因為這事？
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.17,2:23:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那個時候的前輩真的很帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:04.75,2:23:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.68,2:23:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很不錯的人呢
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.77,2:23:14.41,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H000000&\pos(960,1080)}m 0 0 l 1920 0 1920 100 0 100
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.77,2:23:14.41,Default - 2,,0,0,0,,這也不是什麼大事啊...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:14.64,2:23:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對於前輩來說不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,2:23:16.95,2:23:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但對我來說是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,2:23:21.57,2:23:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因為護身符對於我來說 是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.46,2:23:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直這樣帶著它
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.22,2:23:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這個護身符是我奶奶給我的
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.35,2:23:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有了它我的內心才一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.44,2:23:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.22,2:24:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那個時候前輩沒有幫我撿的話
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.66,2:24:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我會很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.62,2:24:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那時前輩還跟我說面試加油呢
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.66,2:24:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有了它我才能放心面試 才能合格
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.75,2:24:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我來到這家公司也是多虧了前輩
